          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For His move on earth we must prepare."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord do grow in us ’til we’re matured in life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As Your army fully qualified."
            }
